React  its two types
 . function components
 . Class Components

Function Components
    function name(){
    return()
    }

Class Components
    class name extends react.component{
    render(
    return()
    )
    }


Arrow function
It is mainly used in project comparing to function and class components.
Example:
     const Apple = (props) => {
     const{appleinfo}= props;
     const{color,type}=appleinfo;
     return(
         <h2>I am {color} {type} apple</h2>
     )
}
